                                <div class="phototagleft">
                                  
                                </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                                                            <p><b>Erik Gleibermann</b> is a <i>WLT</i> contributing editor, social-justice journalist, literary critic, memoirist, and poet. He has written for the <i>Atlantic, New York Times, Oprah Daily, Washington Post, Guardian, Georgia Review, Kenyon Review, Ploughshares</i>, and numerous other literary journals. His work-in-progress is J<i>ewfro American: An Interracial Memoir</i>.<em> </em></p>

